snippet: Isaiah Thomas had 17 points and seven assists to help the Boston Celtics hold off the Detroit Pistons 102-95 on Wednesday night....
lead_paragraph: Isaiah Thomas had 17 points and seven assists to help the Boston Celtics hold off the Detroit Pistons 102-95 on Wednesday night.

headline.main: Thomas Scores 17 as Celtics Stave Off Pistons' Rally, 102-95
